Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.development

Class DevelopmentCard

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.development.DevelopmentCard
All Implemented Interfaces:
AcceptsSupplies, HasStatus, WinPointsCountable
public class DevelopmentCard extends Object implements HasStatus, WinPointsCountable, AcceptsSupplies
This class represents the development card of the game. Every card has its own unique id and has level, win points, category, production and cost.
